These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-1::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: thriller, musical, spy
The people use 3 different means of transport: airplane, ship, van
1. the person watching thriller movies is the person driving the ship##1
2. the person driving the van is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
3. the person driving the van is on the left or right of the person watching musical movies##3
4. the person driving the ship is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller | spy | musical    |
| Transport     | ship    | van       | airplane |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-2::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  paramedic, musician, firefighter
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: snowboarding, soccer, climbing
1. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left of the person who's sport is soccer##1
2. the firefighter is on the left of the paramedic##1
3. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the far left or far right##3
4. the musician is the person who's sport is climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1   |     2     |     3      |
| Job     | firefighter | paramedic | musician  |
| Sport   | snowboarding  | soccer  | climbing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-3::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  scientist, architect, mechanic
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: rock, indie, gospel
1. the fan of indie is on the far left or far right##3
2. the scientist is on the far right##1
3. the architect is the fan of gospel##1
4. the fan of indie is on the right of the fan of gospel##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |     3      |
| Job           | mechanic | architect | scientist |
| Music-Genre   | rock        | gospel    | indie        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-4::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: magic-tricks, hiking, reading
3 different pets are kept: frog, turtle, ferret
1. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
2. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is hiking##3
3. the owner of the frog is between the person who's hobby is reading and the owner of the ferret##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |   3    |
| Hobby   | reading | hiking | magic-tricks |
| Pet     | turtle  | frog    | ferret  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-5::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: musical, time-travel, sports
The people use 3 different means of transport: skateboard, car, jet-ski
1. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left or right of the person watching musical movies##3
2. the person driving the car is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1
3. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the person watching musical movies##1
4. the person watching musical movies is between the person watching time-travel movies and the person driving the jet-ski##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3    |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel | musical | sports |
| Transport     | car   | skateboard   | jet-ski   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-6::.
