3. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##3
4. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the right of the electrician##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |   2    |     3      |
| Hobby   | video-games | sudoku | collecting      |
| Job     | electrician  | firefighter | analyst |

