There are 3 different nationalities: canadian, british, indian
1. the fan of classical is on the right of the british##1
2. the indian is on the left of the fan of punk##1
3. the indian is on the left or right of the fan of hip-hop##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2     |     3      |
