.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-8::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, tea, lemonade
There 3 different types of food: papaya, peas, avocado
1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the person eating papaya##1
2. the person eating peas is in the middle##1
3. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
4. the person drinking tea is on the left or right of the person eating papaya##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |   3    |
| Beverage   | lemonade        | tea  | hot-chocolate   |
| Food       | avocado | peas | papaya |

