2. the dutch is the person drinking soy-milk##1
3. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
4. the pakistani is on the left or right of the person drinking iced-tea##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3    |
| Beverage      | soy-milk    | fanta    | iced-tea  |
| Nationality   | dutch | pakistani | malaysian |

