.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-13::.
There are 3 different nationalities: indonesian, australian, german
3 different pets are kept: goat, fish, bird
1. the owner of the goat is on the far left or far right##3
2. the german is on the right of the owner of the fish##1
3. the owner of the bird is between the owner of the fish and the owner of the goat##2
4. the owner of the goat is the australian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3     |
| Nationality   | indonesian | german | australian |
| Pet           | fish    | bird    | goat       |

