3. the person who's sport is rugby is the person who's sport is rugby##1
4. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |    2     |    3    |
| Hobby   | filmmaking    | skydiving   | drawing |
| Sport   | soccer | rugby | lacrosse |

