3. the fan of soul is on the right of the fan of disco##1
4. the fan of hip-hop is the person watching superhero movies##1
5. the fan of disco is on the left or right of the person watching scientific movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |   2    |     3     |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster | scientific | superhero |
| Music-Genre   | disco     | soul  | hip-hop    |

