.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-20::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, cola, juice
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: epic, action, zombie
1. the person watching action movies is on the left or right of the person drinking juice##3
2. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person watching epic movies##1
3. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person watching action movies##1
4. the person watching zombie movies is on the left of the person drinking cola##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |      3      |
| Beverage      | juice    | cola | iced-tea         |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie | action  | epic |

 